Pull Klex with lava bolt and send in pet.  Kite klex until he turns on the pet.  At this point, I sometimes tried Scars of Sigil to get Klex's attention again, but usually I didn't have time.  It's hard to see exactly ehn Klex turns on the pet due to the fact that you're kiting and trying very hard not to draw adds.  Most of the time my pet was at 50% or so by the time I got back to him and I needed to start thinking about chaining another pet into the fray.<br>
<br>
